Packages 
Package Description
EClass
Package EClass contains all other subpackages needed for the EClass functionality.
EClass.ApprovalTracker
Package ApprovalTracker defines objects and operations related to the approval tracker functionality available to the student and presenter.
EClass.Forum
Package Forum pertains to the objects and operations related to the Forum.
EClass.Person
Package Person defines objects and operations related to any user of the EClass.
EClass.Presentation
Package Presentation defines objects and operations related to the presentation's content.
EClass.Presentation.LayerObject
Package LayerObject defines objects and operations related to the various objects that are drawn or placed on a layer.
